Varada Sethu https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Varada_Sethu 0 Varada Sethu is a British actress, best known for playing DS Mishal Ali in the BBC apocalyptic TV Series Hard Sun. She has also featured in Now You See Me 2 as the assistant to Michael Caine’s character.
